<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.1.8">
<l>kuṇaṅko ṇiṟaipukaḻ maṉṉark koṭaikkaṭaṉ pūṇṭirun</l>
<l>tiṇaṅki yulakuṭa ṉākkilu māṅkava ṉaiyillār</l>
<l>maṇaṅkoṇṭa kōpattu maṉṉiyu mīḷvarkaṇ mīḷvillai</l>
<l>paṇaṅko ḷaravaṇai yāṉṟiru nāmam paṭimiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kings of meritorious full fame, even if they keep taking on the duty of giving,</l>
<l>comply [and] let the world together be [prosperous?], those who are there without him(?),</l>
<l>although they will last in the fury that takes union(?), for those who return there is not return.</l>
<l>Settle for the sacred names of the one on the hooded serpent bed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
